        <abstract> 
<p>Would be interesting to discuss political economy in light of evolution. Recommends Walter Bagehot <hi rend="italic">Physics and politics</hi> [1872] and <hi rend="italic">Descent</hi> in which source of moral sense is discussed.</p> 
